snippet.title: last seen online - now released!
snippet.description:
Play now! http://lastseenonline.com/

No download required, works on your phone.

🔴 last seen online

You were always a snoop, weren’t you? That’s why you bought an old computer you saw lying among piles of junk at a garage sale. You didn’t even bother to format the computer before you turned it on. You were curious. After all, a personal computer is an extension of another person’s soul, all their secrets, projects, interactions.

“last seen online” is a psychological horror escape room, based on early flash games. You play as yourself, looking through someone else’s computer. Solve puzzles and discover the secrets that lie within the computer.

It has always been a dream for me to release a horror game and glad that I finally got to this point! Hope you guys enjoy this.
